data.description: SELLER IS NOW OFFERING $5,000.00 USE AS YOU CHOOSE. NO HOA! No CITY TAXES! Welcome to your dream farmhouse-style retreat! This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is the perfect blend of country living and modern comfort. Step inside and feel the warmth of a space where every corner is filled with natural light and a welcoming vibe. The heart of the home is the spacious living area, perfect for game nights or cozy evenings with loved ones. The kitchen, with its ample counter space and storage, is a cook's delight, making meal prep a breeze and entertaining a joy. Each of the 3 bedrooms is a cozy haven, promising restful nights and energized mornings. The two bathrooms mean no waiting in line during those busy morning routines! Enjoy relaxing in the evening as the air tub gently massages away the stress from the day. It is a must see! Did I mention the 2 BONUS ROOMS?! The large bonus room is a versatile space that can be anything you need - a media room, a playroom for the kids, or even a gym for your daily workouts. The smaller bonus room can be used for a home office or storage. Step outside onto the oversized patio and grill up your favorites while taking in the beautiful trees and landscape on your private lot on the cul-de-sac. This expansive yard is a blank canvas for your gardening dreams. Imagine sipping lemonade on your porch while the sunset paints the sky. This home isn't just a place to live; it's where life's moments happen. It's ready and waiting for you to start your next chapter. So, why wait? Schedule your showing today and come see why this should be your next ''Home Sweet Home.''
